title: Zombies shuffle downtown for World Zombie Day 2015
text:
Undead gather at Hemming Plaza for World Zombie Day. Susan Acosta. View all 20 photos Yesterday marked Jacksonville Zombie Walk 's 8th annual World Zombie Day. October is domestic violence awareness month so this year all proceeds (donations of non-perishable food items, clothing, toys or cash) go to Hubbard House . Brain-eaters gathered at Hemming Plaza for a Carnival of the Dead, including costume contests, photographers, entertainment, food trucks, vendors, and a blood refreshing station. In memory of Grace Katich (Lola Ivelsy), without whom the zombie walk would not have grown to where it is today.
See slideshow above for a glimpse into the blood, fun and general mayhem.
Vendors included Woodley Special Effects LLC , SailorGirl Accessories , Lucky D Studios , Old Skool Junk , Germ Spider Designs , Fallen Asher Designs , Cherry Bomb Charmers Junior Roller Derby , Thrill the World Jacksonville and Umbrella Corporation Jacksonville (Home of the 219th Brain Surgeons) .
